&lt;p&gt;In Canada, the Base compensation range for this role is CAD 186,368&lt;span data-sheets-root=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;- CAD 223,642. Actual compensation may vary based on level, experience, and skillset as assessed in the interview process. Benefits include equity, bonus (if applicable) and other benefits listed&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://grafana.com/about/careers/#jobs&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All of our roles include Restricted Stock Units (RSUs), giving every team member ownership in Grafana Labs&#39; success. We believe in shared outcomes—RSUs help us stay aligned and invested as we scale globally.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;
